payload.content: Had a great meeting with Sarah about the Feed feature. We decided to rename it from 'school-update' to just 'feed' for clarity. Need to update docs and tell the team.
Sarah mentioned the Feed feature again today. She thinks it's going to be a key part of the Willow project. The feature belongs to the Willow education platform.
Working on the Feed implementation today. Need to finish the API endpoints before the demo. This is blocked by the authentication work that Mike is doing.
Reflecting on the decision to use React for the Feed UI. Based on what we learned from the WaterOS project, this should help us move faster. The team is excited about the approach.
Met with the entire Willow team today. Discussed roadmap for Q4. The Feed feature is our top priority. Sarah is leading the effort with help from Mike and the design team.
